data.description: This well-kept, all brick ranch is perfect for the first-time buyer or owner looking to downsize. You'll love having 3 bedrooms and 1 bath all on the same floor. Newer roof, new paint throughout and new dishwasher make this home move in ready! Back yard is large, fenced in and perfect for pets, kids, entertaining or your very own garden. Come see for yourself and schedule your appointment today.
